WEBVTT

00:08:57.040 --> 00:09:02.440
It is estimated that the Dutch produce
4.3 billion tulip bulbs every year.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:07.256
In 2015, two dams collapsed

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:09.976
at an iron ore mine
in southeastern Brazil,

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:12.616
causing one of the worst
environmental disasters

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:14.069
in the history of the country.

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:18.376
It is estimated that 62 million
cubic meters of waste

00:09:18.400 --> 00:09:20.096
were released when the dams broke,

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:22.536
destroying numerous villages
in the process,

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:25.560
including Bento Rodrigues,
seen here before ...

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:29.960
and after the flood.